			<node ID="ID_627504853" TEXT="Systems programming or system programming is the activity of programming computer system software.The primary distinguishing characteristic of systems programming when compared to application programming is that application programming aims to produce software which provides services to the user directly (e.g. word processor) whereas systems programming aims to produce software and software " />
